              <!--  Text: [begin] --> 
              <p>UK/EU&nbsp;fees (PT): &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;£6,010 for 2017/18</p> 
              <!--  Text: [end] --> 
             </div> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27710/text [end] --> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27714/text [begin] --> 
             <div id="c27714" class="csc-default"> 
              <!--  Text: [begin] --> 
              <p>Overseas fees (FT): £25,890 for 2017/18</p> 
              <!--  Text: [end] --> 
             </div> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27714/text [end] --> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27719/text [begin] --> 
             <div id="c27719" class="csc-default"> 
              <!--  Text: [begin] --> 
              <p>Overseas fees (PT): £12,950 for 2017/18</p> 
              <!--  Text: [end] --> 
             </div> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27719/text [end] --> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27720/text [begin] --> 
             <div id="c27720" class="csc-default"> 
              <!--  Text: [begin] --> 
              <p>For a comprehensive list of the funding opportunities available at UCL, including funding relevant to your nationality, please visit the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ucl.ac.uk/prospective-students/scholarships" title="Opens external link in new window" target="_top">Scholarship and Funding website</a>. </p> 
              <p>If you are holding an offer from the Department of Computer Science at UCL, you may be eligible for our <a href="prospective_students/csexcel/" title="Opens internal link in current window" class="internal-link">Excellence Scholarship</a>.</p> 
              <!--  Text: [end] --> 
             </div> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:27720/text [end] --> 
             <!--  CONTENT ELEMENT, uid:29719/textpic [begin] --> 
             <div id="c29719" class="csc-default"> 
              <!--  Header: [begin] --> 
              <div class="csc-header csc-header-n6">
               <h1>Tuition Fee Deposit</h1>
              </div> 
              <!--  Header: [end] --> 
              <!--  Image block: [begin] --> 
              <div class="csc-textpic-text"> 
               <!--  Text: [begin] --> 
               <p>This programme requires that applicants firmly accepting their offer pay a deposit. This allows UCL to effectively plan student numbers, as students are more demonstrably committed towards commencing their studies with us. </p> 
               <p>For full details about the UCL tuition fee deposit, <a href="https://www.ucl.ac.uk/prospective-students/graduate/taught/fees-funding/tuition-fee-deposits" title="Opens external link in new window" target="_top" class="external-link-new-window">please see the central UCL pages</a>. </p> 
               <p>Tuition fee deposits within the Department of Computer Science are currently listed as:</p>
               <table class="">
                <tbody>
                 <tr>
                  <th colspan="2">UK/EU</th>
                  <th colspan="2">Overseas</th>
                 </tr> 
                 <tr>
                  <th>Full-time</th>
                  <th>*Part-time</th>
                  <th>Full-time</th>
                  <th>*Part-time</th> 
                 </tr>
                </tbody>
                <tbody> 
                 <tr> 
                  <td class="align-center">£2000</td>
                  <td class="align-center">£1000</td>
                  <td class="align-center">£2000</td>
                  <td class="align-center">£1000</td> 
                 </tr>
                 <tr>
                  <td colspan="4">&nbsp;</td>
                 </tr> 
                 <tr>
                  <td colspan="4">*where part-time is an available mode of study</td>
                 </tr> 
                </tbody>
               </table> 
               <!--  Text: [end] --> 
              </div> 
              <!--  Image block: [end] --> 
             </div> 
